title: Roger Waters - 2015-10-16 - Music Heals - Washington DC
description:
Another recent Roger Waters performance in my bootleg archive. Very nice recording.

Please enjoy, share with friends and seed please :) Info as per below:
======================================================================

Music Heals, a benefit concert in aid of MusiCorps 
With Billy Corgan, Tom Morello, Jake Clemons & G.E. Smith and featuring the MusiCorps Band 
October 16, 2015
DAR Constitution Hall
Washington DC

Recorded by JB
Edited by Kathleen

Lineage: CA 11 Mics/CA 9100 Preamp > Edirol R9 > Adobe Audition > CD Wave > Trader's Little Helper (FLAC)
